meta_title: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section
short_description: Extends and collapses easily with durable buttons Made of a lightweight and durable aluminum alloy Anodized parts are imprinted with special weather resistant and corrosion resistant inks Sectional junctions are injection molded from a durable, light, impact-resistant plastic Front and back, easy to read scale Scale on back permits easy height readings at eye level Rod Dimensions: 36.8 x 2.6 x 1.8 inches
summary: CST's telescoping aluminum rods are made of a light & durable aluminum alloy.  The anodized  segments are imprinted with exceptional weather resistant and corrosion resistant inks.  Tight tolerances on extruded aluminum parts allow for smooth extension and  deter  unnecessary clattering and slopiness.  The sectional junctions are injection molded from a durable lightweight impact-resistant plastic.  Rods are equipped with  dependable  and wear resistant polycarbonate buttons that  secure  each section.  Easy to read graduations and and a special measuring scale on the rear side allow users to read height at eye level.

short_description: Magnetically-dampened, wire-hung compensator for optimum range and accuracy Compensator lock protects instrument during transport or storage, also acts as a handy compenstor checking tool Large effective aperture and minimum focus of 1 foot (0.3m)
summary: These units now incorporate easy-to-grip styling and an improved compensator. Designed for the contractor, surveyor, or engineer who demands accurate leveling every time, SAL automatic levels set up fast, are easy to use, and save time and money on every job. The SAL Series offers your choice of options: magnification, accuracy, and price. 24X SAL Automatic Level Kit; Includes Tripod and Rod Top-mounted optical peep-sight for quick reference Large, easy-to-use precise focusing knob Easy-to-read horizontal circle Right angle prism for easy bubble viewing Sealed, dust-protected leveling screws Water-resistant, sealed construction plus sunshade for use in various weather conditions Fine motion knobs on left and right sides with friction-braked rotation, endless horizontal drive. 1:100 stadia for distance estimation 5/8-11 threads to fit standard tripods Available in 360 degrees or 400 gons; please specify Includes hardshell carrying case with dual latches, plumb bob, Allen wrench, adjusting pin, and instruction manual.
